article.headline: McLaughlin scores 19, Northern Arizona knocks off Seattle U 62-60
article.description: — Trenton McLaughlin scored 19 points as Northern Arizona beat Seattle U 62-60 on Wednesday.
article.linkText: McLaughlin scores 19, Northern Arizona knocks off Seattle U 62-60
article.story: SEATTLE -- — Trenton McLaughlin scored 19 points as Northern Arizona beat Seattle U 62-60 on Wednesday. McLaughlin added six rebounds and four steals for the Lumberjacks (1-2). Rockwell Reynolds scored 13 points and added seven rebounds. Carson Basham finished 5 of 6 from the floor to finish with 10 points. The Redhawks (2-1) were led in scoring by Alex Schumacher, who finished with 24 points, six rebounds and four assists. Cameron Tyson added 14 points for Seattle U. In addition, Vasja Pandza had eight points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
